  "update_summary": "Visual overhaul: metric-true procedural CMU, ivory-buff brick, and corrugated PBR tiles (life-size blocks instead of miniature tiling), a redesigned 2048x512 tower-mounted cabinet sign with cannonball badge, DIN lockup, tagline pill, and cannon finial, new parapet/coping, pilasters, wainscot, clearance bar, menu monument, bollards, exit accents, and rooftop equipment, plus a cyclic ambient animation flag so the rollers keep spinning the entire time any vehicle is in the wash.",
